Package: secret
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: @MAINTAINER@
Installed-Size: @INSTALLED_SIZE@
Depends: libc6, git, gnupg
Recommends: pass, qrencode, openssh-client
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/nostra124/secret
Description: Multi-store GPG-encrypted secret manager
 secret manages GPG-encrypted-at-rest secrets across multiple
 git-backed stores, with pass(1) integration and SSH sync between
 peers. Each store is a git repository and each parameter is
 encrypted to the store's recipients.
 .
 This package also ships libsecstore (shared and static) and its
 public header for embedding the secret store engine in other tools.
